        <item>
            <title>Version 0.6</title>
			<description><![CDATA[
							<ul>
								<li><strong>NEW:</strong> Chromecast support! You can now stream Apple event videos on your Chromecast.</li>
								<li><strong>FIXED:</strong> Failure to load events when the system used a 12-hour clock.</li>
								<li><strong>FIXED:</strong> Visual anomaly with tabs on 10.12.</li>
								<li><strong>FIXED:</strong> Improved performance on 10.12.</li>
							</ul>
						]]></description>
            <pubDate>Sun, 23 Oct 2016 21:35:00 -0200</pubDate>
